        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/ci-management-jjb-verify/975/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/ci-management-jjb-verify/975",
